{"id":2,"date":"2024-03-12T13:21:06","date_gmt":"2024-03-12T13:21:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/?page_id=2"},"modified":"2024-04-03T14:14:54","modified_gmt":"2024-04-03T14:14:54","slug":"sisr","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/sisr\/","title":{"rendered":"SISR"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border is-style-default wp-duotone-unset-1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003721736.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-50\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-radius:100px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003721736.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003721736-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-medium-font-size is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-1 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-width:12px;border-radius:100px\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">SISR signifie \u00ab\u00a0Solutions d\u2019Infrastructure Syst\u00e8mes et R\u00e9seaux\u00a0\u00bb<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">L\u2019option\u00a0<strong>SISR\u00a0<\/strong>est destin\u00e9e aux \u00e9tudiants qui s\u2019orientent vers les<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">m\u00e9tiers li\u00e9s \u00e0 la conception et la maintenance d\u2019infrastructures r\u00e9seaux.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 cette option, l\u2019\u00e9tudiant sera capable de g\u00e9rer de A \u00e0 Z un parc informatique en optimisant les r\u00e9seaux et les syst\u00e8mes : cr\u00e9ation d\u2019applications, int\u00e9gration de logiciels, gestion du mat\u00e9riel, configuration des micro-ordinateurs, etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Cette option vient s\u2019ajouter au tronc commun, comprenant les mati\u00e8res g\u00e9n\u00e9rales (Management, Droit, Anglais, Culture G\u00e9n\u00e9rale et Expression) qui permettront \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tudiant d\u2019\u00eatre \u00e0 l\u2019aise dans son entreprise.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Poursuite d&rsquo;\u00e9tudes :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">&#8211; Licence professionnelle&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">&#8211; Ecole d&rsquo;ing\u00e9nieur<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Voici les d\u00e9bouch\u00e9s possibles avec un BTS SIO SISR :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Technicien de production<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Technicien d\u2019infrastructure<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Technicien r\u00e9seau et t\u00e9l\u00e9coms<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Technicien syst\u00e8mes et r\u00e9seaux<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Administrateur syst\u00e8mes et r\u00e9seaux<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Support syst\u00e8mes et r\u00e9seaux<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Pilote d\u2019exploitation<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">\u2013 Informaticien support et d\u00e9ploiement<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-content-justification-center is-layout-constrained wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>SISR signifie \u00ab\u00a0Solutions d\u2019Infrastructure Syst\u00e8mes et R\u00e9seaux\u00a0\u00bb L\u2019option\u00a0SISR\u00a0est destin\u00e9e aux \u00e9tudiants qui s\u2019orientent vers les m\u00e9tiers li\u00e9s \u00e0 la conception et la maintenance d\u2019infrastructures r\u00e9seaux. Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 cette option, l\u2019\u00e9tudiant sera capable de g\u00e9rer de A \u00e0 Z un parc informatique en optimisant les r\u00e9seaux et les syst\u00e8mes : cr\u00e9ation d\u2019applications, int\u00e9gration de logiciels, gestion [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-2","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"blocksy_meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2"}],"version-history":[{"count":17,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":626,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2\/rev